# Cursor Rules - kombify Mintlify Documentation

## Project Type
Mintlify documentation site (MDX + docs.json). NOT a web app.

## Key Files
- `docs.json` - Site configuration and navigation (Mintlify schema)
- `*.mdx` - Documentation pages with YAML frontmatter
- `_templates/` - Page templates for new content
- `internal-notes/` - Source material (never publish directly)
- `.vscode/mcp.json` - Mintlify MCP server configuration

## Frontmatter (Required on ALL .mdx files)
```yaml
---
title: "Sentence case title"
description: "One-line SEO summary"
---
```

## Brand
- "kombify" (lowercase k, always)
- Tools: "kombify Stack", "kombify Sim", "kombify StackKits", "kombify Sphere"
- Config file: `kombination.yaml`

## Writing
- Second-person voice ("you")
- Sentence-case headings
- Language tags on all code blocks
- Relative internal links without .mdx extension
- Prerequisites at top of procedural content

## Mintlify Components (use in MDX)
- `<Card>` / `<CardGroup cols={N}>` - Navigation cards
- `<Steps>` / `<Step title="">` - Numbered procedures
- `<Tabs>` / `<Tab title="">` - Tabbed content
- `<Accordion>` / `<AccordionGroup>` - Collapsible sections
- `<CodeGroup>` - Multi-language code examples
- `<Note>` / `<Warning>` / `<Tip>` / `<Info>` - Callouts
- `<ParamField>` / `<ResponseField>` - API docs
- `<RequestExample>` / `<ResponseExample>` - API examples

## Navigation (docs.json)
- `tabs` array: product tabs with grouped pages
- `navigation.pages`: main sidebar groups
- Page paths are relative, no .mdx extension

## Validation
```bash
node scripts/validate-frontmatter.js
node scripts/check-links.js
node scripts/check-orphaned-pages.js
node scripts/navigation-coverage.js
```

## Do NOT
- Add pages to `/tools/` (deprecated)
- Use Title Case headings
- Skip frontmatter
- Use absolute URLs for internal links
- Publish internal-notes content without rewriting
